                        <interp inst="t18561027-name-271" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH HART</persName>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> The assignees have not got that book—I have not seen it—it has never been in our possession.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. SERJEANT SHEE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Has Fossey obtained his certificate? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> He has.</p>
