               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185610270065"></xptr>
               <p>I spoke to Fossey on the subject of that counterfoil; I recollect calling his attention to it by saying, "That amount I have nothing to do with"—that was when I was his partner—I do not remember tie date of that con<lb></lb>versation.</p>
